mixin main
    main.main#main
        .main__modalContainer#modalMain
            .main__modalPage 
                .modalExit
                    a.modalPage-exit#modalExit &times;
                .modalPage__wrapper
                    img.modalPage-imgContent#modalPageImg(src="", alt="modalPage image", draggable="false")
                    .modalPage-textContent 
                        p.modalPage__text#modalPageText Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Enim sit scelerisque augue porttitor. Aenean egestas sed fusce arcu sagittis quis lorem. Rhoncus scelerisque velit phasellus ipsum feugiat gravida pulvinar odio. Volutpat cras diam rhoncus quis eu quis sed donec.
        .main__container
            .container__textContent
                h6.textContent-subheading Hello Im 
                h3.textContent-heading SHUKUROV RASHID 
                p.textContent-paragraph This portfolio website serves as a testament to my ongoing development in skills and self-awareness.
                a.textContent-link(href="#") Contact me 
            .container__imgContent
                img.imgContent-mainImg(src="@img/mainMe.png", alt="",draggable="false")
        .main__container2#aboutMe 
            .container__newimgContent 
                img.imgContent-imgMain(src="@img/mainMe2.png", alt="",draggable="false")
            .container__textInfo 
                h6.textContent-info About me
                p.textContent-paragraphInfo
                    strong.paragraphBold Shukurov Rashid 
                    span - I strive to enhance my developer experience and be adaptable across diverse IT fields. I aim to stay relevant in various areas to contribute to innovative projects. I am eager to enrich my IT knowledge and skills by pursuing internships at different companies, where I can learn from professionals and tackle real-world challenges. This practical experience will help me become a more versatile and effective contributor to the tech industry.
                    